import React from 'react'
import {SidebarContainer, Icon, CloseIcon} from './SidebarElements'

const Sidebar = () => {
    return (
        <SidebarContainer>
            <Icon>
                <CloseIcon />
            </Icon>
            <SideBarWrapper>
                <SidebarMenu>
                    <SidebarLink to="included">
                        whats included?
                    </SidebarLink>
                    <SidebarLink to="mission">
                        our mission
                    </SidebarLink>
                    <SidebarLink to="about">
                        about us
                    </SidebarLink>
                    <SidebarLink to="contact">
                        contact us
                    </SidebarLink>
                </SidebarMenu>
                <SideBtnWrap>
                    <SideBarRoute>
                        buy now
                    </SideBarRoute>
                </SideBtnWrap>


            </SideBarWrapper>


        </SidebarContainer>
    )
}

export default Sidebar
